-- France's Bollore starts increasing Mediobanca stake
-- By Danilo Masoni
-- Fri Jul 04, 2014 11:52AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, July 4 (Reuters) - French financier Vincent Bollore has increased his stake in Italian investment bank Mediobanca <MDBI.MI> to 6.46 percent from 6 percent, Mediobanca said in a statement on Friday.

Bollore, who controls the stake through holding company Financiere Du Perguet, has said he wants to increase his stake to 8 percent.